title: Dayton Aviation Heritage National Historical Park: Outdoor Activities
body: Outdoor Activities         A variety of trees are located at the Huffman Prairie Interpretive Center. NPS Photo  Identifying Trees  Learn to ID trees at Wright Memorial at the Huffman Prairie Interpretive Center with our easy to use map and tree list.    View a complete list of trees at Wright Memorial.  Download and print a map of trees at Wright Memorial to accompany your tree list.
